{"tid":1496723,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"葵芳到底做緊乜鳩","createTime":"2019-08-22T15:57:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-22T15:58:56.000Z","uid":267428,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"1872fdd1d5adf5e1c469806deb82ce4d0b47a715","tid":1496723,"uid":267428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T15:57:00.000Z","msg":"無啦啦成班唔俾人俾錢 <br />\n<br />\n得罪講句 真係唔知做乜鳩<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你要搞得兩個方向<br />\n<br />\n一係就向和平理性方向搞<br />\ne.g.靜坐 派傳單<br />\n<br />\n一係就索性向武力嘅方向搞<br />\ne.g.破壞 落閘<br />\n<br />\n兩個都有優點<br />\n<br />\n但最撚憎就係兩頭唔到岸<br />\n<br />\n又唔係用破壞迫使港鐵回應 <br />\n又唔係用和平理性爭取民意支持迫使港鐵回應<br />\n<br />\n搞到變咗唔俾人俾錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你要唔俾人俾錢就索性直接打爛部機算啦<br />\n保證聽日港鐵即刻出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1500902f7519faa25e95e0563878720d6707608","tid":1496723,"uid":267428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T15:58:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9adb555fa66b61c6eb5b738f992bdfba0482f26e","tid":1496723,"uid":267428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T15:58:56.000Z","msg":"推"}]}